Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: sparkpost-ip-notifier
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Package to notify you by email when your External IP has changed.
Home-page: https://github.com/iktw/sparkpost-ip-notifier
Author: Mohammed Hammoud
Author-email: mohammed@iktw.se
License: MIT licence, see LICENSE
Description: # SparkPost IP Notifier
        Package to notify you by email when your External IP has changed.
        
        ## Install package
        ``` pip install sparkpost-ip-notifier ```
        
        ## Usage
        ```
        from sparkpostipnotifier import SparkPostIPNotifier
        
        IPN = SparkPostIPNotifier(
            sparkpost_api_key='mysparkpost-api-key',
            subject='Your NUC IP-address has changed',
            from_email='nuc-ipaddress-notifier@iktw.se',
            recipients=['mohammed@iktw.se']
        )
        ```
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
